WHAT HAPPENS NEXT

If this interview goes well, we'll invite you to a second conversation with our Case Manager. That one covers the supports you might need to succeed in the program, such as transportation, childcare, or technology.

If none of the available times work, reply to this email and we'll find something that does.

We look forward to speaking with you.

The RTS Team at ULEM
